            <div class="approach-inner-content-wrapper one-third">
                <h3 class="approach-section-title">We'll be right&nbsp;<br />there with you</h3>
                <p class="approach-section-text">
                    UX is not a linear, step-by-step process. It’s a way of thinking. It’s solving real problems with empathy.
                </p>
                <p class="approach-section-text">
                    So, make room for us because we’re diving in with you. We have to live it. Breathe it. Obsess over the details. We’re going to ask you questions. We’re going to ask your users questions. We’ll poke. We’ll prod. We’ll make you think. We’ll make you rethink.
                </p>
                <p class="approach-section-text">
                    We walk with you the entire step of the way. We know you may be skeptical, but we’re asking you to trust us. We’re the real deal.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- END approach-section -->

        <section class="approach-section">
            <div class="approach-inner-content-wrapper one-third">
                <h3 class="approach-section-title">We bring the&nbsp;<br />whole gang</h3>
                <p class="approach-section-text">We’re a small group of hungry, talented professionals. There is no B-team: you get our best researchers, architects, designers, and developers. And we’ll give it everything we’ve got.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-inner-block two-third">
